## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **beremagene geperpavec Vyjuvek 2023** = first FDA topical gene therapy in any disease — DEB COL7A1. HSV-1 vector + 만성 wound 적용. Krystal Biotech. paradigm shift — topical repeat-dosing gene therapy 가능. quantum-VQE 의 HSV-1 capsid + COL7A1 cargo packaging fit.
2. **birch bark extract Filsuvez 2023** = first FDA topical botanical for EB junctional + dystrophic. triterpene-rich oleogel. plant-derived natural product 임상 paradigm 한정.
3. **pz-cel / Vyjuvek 2nd-gen + prademagene zamikeracel (PZ-cel) 2024** = Phase 3 RDEB next wave — autologous keratinocyte CRISPR-edited graft + Vyjuvek systemic 확장. 2023 후 broader systemic delivery 가 next horizon.
4. **diacerein topical Phase 3 failed 2024 (Castle Creek)** = EBS IL-1β/MMP 가설 falsified. EBS keratin dominant-negative direct target 이 더 직접적.
5. **D-FFP-2 (Wings Therapeutics) Phase 3** = recombinant collagen VII IV protein replacement — gene therapy 와 alternative. systemic deliver + half-life + immunogenicity 가 open question.
6. **gentamicin systemic read-through stop codon** = RDEB nonsense mutation 일부 read-through 가능 — 임상 evidence 약함 + nephrotoxicity/ototoxicity. ELX-02 + ataluren 차세대 read-through 가 next.
7. **RDEB SCC 만성 cancer 위험** = 35세+ RDEB 환자 사망원인 1위 (cumulative incidence > 50%). 만성 wound + chronic inflammation + UV-independent SCC. cetuximab + cemiplimab + pembrolizumab 임상 cross-cancer.
8. **합병증 spectrum** = 만성 esophageal stricture + pseudosyndactyly (mitten deformity) + cardiomyopathy + anemia + osteoporosis + nutritional deficit + 만성 통증. 만성 systemic phenotype.
9. **K-EB 임상 framework** = 식약처 + 산정특례 (희귀질환) + DEBRA Korea 환자단체 + 한국 EB 환자 200-300명 추정 (RDEB severe ~50명). Vyjuvek 한국 도입 미정 (2026 시점).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, EB 임상 의미 한정. RDEB SCC 만성 cancer + 만성 wound + 만성 systemic 합병증 cross-disease overlap 광범위.

